Name: TypeOfAudioClip
Description: The type of audio clip provided. Supports the use of a controlled vocabulary.

Name: AudioClipBegin
Description: The point to begin the audio clip. If no point is provided the assumption is that the start point is the beginning of the clip provided.

Name: AudioClipEnd
Description: The point to end the audio clip. If no point is provided the assumption is that the end point is the end of the clip provided.
